lead_paragraph: Villarreal's poor run continued as they were held 0-0 at home by Real Sociedad in La Liga and Paco Alcacer's late equaliser rescued a point for Valencia in a 2-2 draw at troubled Getafe on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Villarreal Held by Sociedad, Valencia Dent Getafe Survival Bid
